@startuml seq-realtime-merge
' Context: messaging
' Profile: client
' Event: RealtimeReceived, DeliveryTickReceived
' SDD: PROM-REALTIME-OWNER, PROM-MESSAGE-STATUS
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title seq-realtime-merge — aggiornamento realtime conversazione

participant "Supabase Realtime" as RT
participant "RealtimeAttachmentMachine" as RAM
participant "ConversationLoadMachine" as CLM
participant "UI" as UI

RT -> RAM : RealtimeReceived
RAM -> CLM : merge message\n(Ready state)

alt tick-only (sole spunte)
  CLM -> CLM : DeliveryTickReceived\npreserve content/media
else nuovo contenuto
  CLM -> CLM : merge by client_message_id
end

CLM --> UI : list updated

note over CLM
  Una sola bolla per client_message_id.
  Merge in place — no duplicate bubbles.
end note

@enduml
